## âš¡ Quick Start

### Option 1: Using Scripts (Windows)
```bash
# Install dependencies
scripts\install.bat

# Start server
scripts\run.bat
```

### Option 2: Manual
```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Start server
python server.py
```

### Option 3: Test Everything
```bash
python scripts\test_api.py
```

